{
  "texts": [
    "30 have implemented a Teaching-Learning-Prediction (TLP) mechanism to study and predict the intentions of human hand-over and also the multi-modal demonstration.",
    "In the developed mechanism, a robot was programmed by humans using different demonstrations using natural language.",
    "Moreover, the wearable sensors were used based on human working preferences and task needs.",
    "Here, the Extreme Learning Machine (ELM) was used to upgrade the capacity of cognition which permitted the robot to utilize the learned policy to recognize the human intention efficiently.",
    "At last, different experiments were performed to display the effectualness of the implemented technique over classical models."
  ]
}